card_notes.note:
Choose the habitat that sustains.

Koala is the memory of the body: routines, safety, familiarity. It appears when you must honor your pace.

See what’s toxic.

Stay deep, then rise when called.

Port Jackson is the deep witness that doesn’t chase. It waits, it knows, it remains.

Moment arrives.

Stop pretending. Start cleansing.

Tasmanian Devil appears when denial is over. It brings raw reality, cleansing by confrontation.

Instant truth.

advice: Truth arrives fast. The window is short. Act cleanly and decisively.
Treat this as guidance, not a fixed outcome.
